387
00:20:26,236 --> 00:20:27,767
- Sugar?
- Thank you.

388
00:20:28,501 --> 00:20:30,604
Thank you so much
for having us to dinner.

389
00:20:30,605 --> 00:20:31,788
Our pleasure.

390
00:20:32,243 --> 00:20:35,948
I always like to get to know my new
associates and their significant others.

391
00:20:35,949 --> 00:20:38,423
Well, we really
appreciate the invitation.

392
00:20:38,424 --> 00:20:39,596
It's our pleasure.

393
00:20:40,192 --> 00:20:41,286
It's fun for us, two.

394
00:20:44,244 --> 00:20:45,759
I'm really sorry about David.

395
00:20:45,760 --> 00:20:48,027
I think he's still upset about Katie.

396
00:20:48,620 --> 00:20:49,725
He's lovely.

397
00:20:49,981 --> 00:20:52,396
But he's started his surgical rotation.

398
00:20:52,415 --> 00:20:55,096
He's doing these endless shifts.
He's very sleep-deprived.

399
00:20:55,097 --> 00:20:58,339
I really understand,
but I don't think it's just that.

400
00:20:59,351 --> 00:21:00,351
