00:21:11,214 --> 00:21:12,411
We're bred for it.

405
00:21:13,475 --> 00:21:15,884
Men can't do it.

406
00:21:16,209 --> 00:21:17,245
At least,

407
00:21:17,539 --> 00:21:20,044
not the ones worth
sharing a bed with.

408
00:21:22,117 --> 00:21:23,916
We got to go. I got work.

409
00:21:25,225 --> 00:21:26,261
Biscotti?

