00:21:49,239 --> 00:21:50,320
I answered her question.

422
00:21:50,321 --> 00:21:52,532
No, you grunted like a caveman.

423
00:21:53,166 --> 00:21:54,805
I answered her, didn't I?

424
00:21:55,439 --> 00:21:57,063
I had to apologize for you.

425
00:21:57,341 --> 00:21:58,418
You what?

426
00:22:05,104 --> 00:22:06,990
You can't do this to me, David.

427
00:22:07,933 --> 00:22:09,745
Patty knew you were miserable.

428
00:22:10,951 --> 00:22:12,528
These events are part my job.

429
00:22:12,529 --> 00:22:14,279
- There are going to be more.
- I get it.

430
00:22:14,756 --> 00:22:17,941
Patty's your boss. That doesn't
mean that I have to like her.

431
00:22:23,935 --> 00:22:24,935
Hello?

432
00:22:28,308 --> 00:22:29,437
<i>Hello.</i>

433
00:22:30,288 --> 00:22:32,481
- <i>Who is this?</i>
- It's Gregory Malina.

434
00:22:34,677 --> 00:22:35,749
I want to talk.

435
00:22:43,965 --> 00:22:45,806
Where did you meet David Connor?

436
00:22:47,497 --> 00:22:48,497
At the hospital.

437
00:22:48,810 --> 00:22:49,936
Where he worked?

438
00:22:50,437 --> 00:22:52,142
David treated my grandfather.

439
00:22:53,217 --> 00:22:54,903
I'm sorry.
I just can't believe this.

440
00:22:55,057 --> 00:22:57,206
Miss Dimeo,
how long were you dating David Connor?

441
00:22:57,207 --> 00:22:58,815
Almost four months.

442
00:23:01,366 --> 00:23:02,501
What?

443
00:23:03,021 --> 00:23:06,834
Any idea why Ellen Parsons
didn't move out until two days ago?

444
00:23:07,216 --> 00:23:09,242
She moved out the day
she found out about us.

445
00:23:09,243 --> 00:23:11,856
So David Connor was cheating
on Miss Parsons with you?

446
00:23:13,912 --> 00:23:15,752
3 1/2 MONTHS EARLIER

