00:23:18,217 --> 00:23:19,884
- Can I take your jacket?
- Yeah.

448
00:23:20,147 --> 00:23:21,373
Thank you.

449
00:23:21,941 --> 00:23:23,116
Oh, thanks.

450
00:23:25,319 --> 00:23:26,804
Caught up there.

451
00:23:27,206 --> 00:23:28,626
Sorry.

452
00:23:33,024 --> 00:23:35,083
Oh, that's me and my parents.

