welcoming everybody.

487
00:25:34,255 --> 00:25:35,522
It's bullshit.

488
00:25:36,341 --> 00:25:38,135
She don't look after anybody.

489
00:25:38,800 --> 00:25:39,947
No, she doesn't.

490
00:25:40,868 --> 00:25:42,631
You got to look out for yourself.

491
00:25:43,527 --> 00:25:46,172
When I first moved here,
I thought I'd just, you know,

492
00:25:46,636 --> 00:25:48,677
figure out what I was good at.

493
00:25:49,218 --> 00:25:50,383
And?

494
00:25:50,679 --> 00:25:53,247
Turns out the only talent
I have is getting people to like me.

495
00:25:55,071 --> 00:25:56,199
This is crazy.

496
00:25:57,623 --> 00:26:00,677
This all comes down to getting
attention of someone at a bar.

497
00:26:01,620 --> 00:26:02,826
I'm glad you called.

498
00:26:02,827 --> 00:26:04,627
Yeah, you're glad I called.

499
00:26:04,952 --> 00:26:06,874
- What?
